column5: Loonietoon, (Kelvin) and I will be at the Firehall in Bronte tomorrow evening from 6.00pm until ? Any and all are welcome to join us.  John...
hey John just so happens work brings me out that way tommorow - i finish around 7-8pm tho... i think i'll stop in for a pint
I wouldn't mind at all, but can't make it tomorrow night. Don't forget the weather is looking like it'll be nasty.  Have a good time if you go and drive safe.
